text: Gerard Theodor Hubert van Innis was an archer from Belgium. Innis competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1920 Summer Olympics.Hubert VAN INNIS He was born on 24 February 1866 and died on 25 November 1961.Hubert Van Innis == References == Category:1866 births Category:1961 deaths Category:Belgian archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for Belgium Category:Olympic silver medalists for Belgium
